<h1>Set person as Out of office (absent)</h1>

<p>The window allows you to set the current or future absence of the user.</p>
<p>Options:</p>
	<ul>
 <li><strong>Out of office since</strong> - enter the date and time from which the user will be or is absent.</li>
 <li><strong>Out of office until</strong> - enter the date and time until which the user will be absent.</li>
	</ul>

</asp:Content>
